---
// ============================================
// SABERO Consulting - Nosotros CTA
// ============================================
---

<section class="ns-cta" data-reveal>
  <div class="ns-cta-glow"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="ns-cta-title">Construyamos algo grande juntos</h2>
    <p class="ns-cta-p">Conversa con nuestro equipo y descubre cómo podemos impulsar tu próximo proyecto.</p>
    <div class="ns-cta-actions">
      <a href="/contacto/" class="ns-cta-btn">
        Conversemos
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M1 8h14M8 1l7 7-7 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      </a>
      <a href="/#oferta" class="ns-cta-btn ns-cta-btn--b">
        Ver capacidades
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ns-cta {
    position: relative;
    padding: 60px 0;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--color-deep-blue);
  }
  .ns-cta-glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: -30%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 700px;
    height: 600px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.12), transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .ns-cta-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .ns-cta-p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto 40px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .ns-cta-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .ns-cta-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 16px 36px;
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-white);
    background: var(--color-electric-blue);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.3);
  }
  .ns-cta-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.4);
    background: var(--color-electric-blue-hover);
  }
  .ns-cta-btn svg {
    transition: transform var(--transition-base);
  }
  .ns-cta-btn:hover svg {
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }
  .ns-cta-btn--b {
    background: transparent;
    box-shadow: none;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
  }
  .ns-cta-btn--b:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.24);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .ns-cta { padding: 64px 0; }
  }
</style>
